HCR 99 Original 2026 Regular Session Kerner
Creates the La. Electronic Monitoring and GPS Oversight Task Force to study and make
recommendations relative to statewide oversight, infrastructure, reporting, accountability,
investigative duties, provider duties, and public safety standards for electronic monitoring
and GPS monitoring in La.
Requires the task force to submit its findings and recommendations to the legislature within
one year of adoption of the Resolution.
